fulltitle: "Talk Across America" Guest Jazz Legend Dick Hyman
description: Doug Miles talks with jazz legend Dick Hyman about playing in the Sarasota Jazz Festival, working with Ken Peplowski, the state of jazz, different styles of jazz piano and more in this conversation as aired WTMY 1280 AM Sarasota. (www.dougmilesmedia.com)
